<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xmlns:frus="http://history.state.gov/frus/ns/1.0"><text><body><div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1920-03-16T19:34:00-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1920-03-16T19:34:00-05:00" n="689" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d689">
                            <note rend="inline" type="source">861.77/1429: Telegram</note>
                            <head><hi rend="italic">The Consul at Harbin</hi> (<persName type="from"><hi rend="italic">Jenkins</hi></persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Acting Secretary of
                                        State</gloss></hi></head>
                            <opener><dateline rendition="#right"><placeName><hi rend="smallcaps">Harbin</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1920-03-17T09:00:00+08:26"><hi rend="italic">March 17,
                                            1920—9 a.m.</hi></date><lb/>[Received 3:23
                                    p.m.]</dateline></opener>
                            <p>Strike will be declared ended 11 o’clock to-day. Horvat has
                                resigned.</p>
                            <closer><signed><hi rend="smallcaps">Jenkins</hi></signed></closer>
                        </div>
                        </body></text></TEI>